text: Eva Rueda (born 13 September 1971) is a Spanish artistic gymnast, born in Madrid. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Madrid Category:Spanish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics
